id=update_blocker
name=Update Blocker
version=v1.9
versionCode=10
author=RAFSuNX
description=Blocks Android OTA updates at the root level. Per-device/Android-version config in devices.json nulls the OTA-apply binary and disables the OTA app package. Does not touch GMS/GSF. Requires the OverlayFS MetaModule (meta-overlayfs). Use the Action button to reset update_engine and clear OTA cache.
